&lt;div class=&quot;lP_Content&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Step 2: The 5 Key Questions&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
If any wellbeing indicators are identified the following 5 key questions will help practitioners decide what action, if any, is required:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;SP1_AdvancedBlue&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. What is getting in the way of this child or young person&amp;#39;s wellbeing?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Do I have all the information I need to help this child or young person?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. What can I do now to help this child or young person?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. What can my agency do to help this child or young person?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. What additional help, if any, may be needed from others?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;clear: both;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;div.SP1_AdvancedBlue { 
