	&lt;li&gt;State what the Getting It Right for Every Child (GIRFEC) approach is&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Recognise the National Practice model&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Recognise the importance of managing wellbeing concerns&lt;/li&gt;
